        OC -->|0.60 - 0.84<br/>Medium Confidence| ENHANCED[Enhanced Review<br/>• Additional Evidence Request<br/>• Cross-Reference Checking<br/>• Supervisor Review]
        
        OC -->|< 0.60<br/>Low Confidence| MANUAL[Manual Investigation<br/>• Identity Verification<br/>• Evidence Authentication<br/>• Fraud Assessment]
    end
    
    subgraph "Continuous Learning"
        FEEDBACK[Decision Outcome<br/>Feedback Loop]
        TUNING[Threshold Adjustment<br/>& Algorithm Improvement]
        
        AUTO --> FEEDBACK
        ENHANCED --> FEEDBACK
        MANUAL --> FEEDBACK
        FEEDBACK --> TUNING
        TUNING --> CA
    end
    
